title: My Indigo
typeOfFood: Chinese, Japanese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Asian fusion restaurant chain offering mixed cuisines with mainly curries, stir-fries, and sushi. Customers could mix-and-match elements of the main courses and choose the spicy level. This outlet is at the food court of the Frankfurt central train station.
